name: Dubhop
description: Music has always played such an integral part in Fluf culture, starting from the rhythmic beat of the heart and the sound of their mother’s voice when they were just a young Fluflet. As they grew to know the harsh nature of the real world, music and rhythm gave them an escape to a peaceful world where everything vibed with their soul.
